  not in $N[3]$, so $N[3] eq.not V$.
- Any other vertex has even fewer neighbors.
Thus $gamma(G) = 2 > 1 = K$. No dominating set of size 1 exists.

*Target (MinimumSumMulticenter):* Same graph, $w(v) = 1$, $ell(e) = 1$,
