- Center at 0: $d(3, {0}) = 2$, $d(4, {0}) = 3$, $d(5, {0}) = 3$.
  $sum = 0 + 1 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 3 = 10 > 5$.

No single vertex achieves $sum d(v, {p}) lt.eq 5$. #sym.checkmark


